{{define "subject"}}Assignment run completed for {{index .Vars "conferenceName"}}{{end}}
{{define "body"}}
<p>Hi{{with .RecipientName}} {{.}}{{end}},</p>
<p>The assignment algorithm finished for <strong>{{index .Vars "conferenceName"}}</strong>.</p>
<ul style="line-height:1.7;">
  <li>Total assignments produced: <strong>{{index .Vars "assignmentCount"}}</strong></li>
  <li>Objective score: <strong>{{index .Vars "objective"}}</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>Review the proposal and approve in the portal:</p>
<p><a href="{{index .Vars "runLink"}}" style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 18px;background:{{.BrandColor}};color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;">Open assignment studio</a></p>
{{end}}
